    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0

    tmp = 0.0
    tmp = wp.cos(v2)
    v0 = (v1 - v1)
    v0 = ((v2 * (v2 + 0.43 * tmp + 0.83)) - wp.sin(wp.abs(v2 + 0.19)))
    tmp = 0.11
    v2 = wp.sin(0.40)
    data[tid] = v0
